.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/ULDM/111%2c%e9%87%91%e8%a8%b4%2c146%2c20220824%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"ULDM,111,金訴,146,20220824,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"金訴","JNO":"146","JDATE":"20220824","JTITLE":"違反洗錢防制法"}